{"tid":1928832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趁疫情來亂！中共戰機首次深夜遠海長訓擾台　台灣IDF、F-16升空攔截","createTime":"2020-03-16T15:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T01:33:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"680e6cb369e191db7131b9da1fcb40ec34763a4d","tid":1928832,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"趁疫情來亂！中共戰機首次深夜遠海長訓擾台　我IDF、F-16升空攔截<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20200316/1719095/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20200316%2F1719095%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2a6c262a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20200316%2F1719095%2F&h=a19faf7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20200316/1719095/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球都因武漢肺炎疫頭痛之際，中共解放軍今（16日）首度進行深夜遠海長訓擾台！國防部晚間表示，偵獲中共空警500、殲11等型機，於晚間7時許於台灣西南方海域，執行夜間飛行訓練，期間曾接近我防空識別區（ADIZ），經我空中偵巡戰機適切應對，實施廣播驅離後，共機飛離我防空識別區。<br />\n<br />\n國防部強調，國軍運用聯合情監偵作為，對於台海周邊海空域狀況，均能全程監偵，充分掌握與應處，護衛國土安全，籲請國人放心。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，我空軍戰機IDF戰機掀起飛升空攔截，隨後F-16戰機也緊急起飛進行攔截。國防部資深官員指出，解放軍此次深夜出海夜航，航經我西南方空域，這也顯示中共飛行員的夜航能力大增，未來我將24小時遭中共解放軍海空威脅。"},{"pid":"4742b12913f7ae5dc3be189bcbe479c43aded968","tid":1928832,"uid":199957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"咩年代<br />\n有夜航能力唔係好正常？ 仲能力大增？<br />\n假假地支那都話自己有第5代戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堂堂第5代連夜航能力都冇咩"},{"pid":"35ec772e05013dae5bf34bf588b4471ad98c2a7e","tid":1928832,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4742b12913f7ae5dc3be189bcbe479c43aded968","tid":1928832,"uid":199957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"咩年代<br />\n有夜航能力唔係好正常？ 仲能力大增？<br />\n假假地支那都話自己有第5代戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堂堂第5代連夜航能力都冇咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"吹敵人勁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a76d9627d54e1ac6da2a3691be48dcacd28341e","tid":1928832,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"一趁亂就搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5d65ac9ba4bc0729c96e5b297ae7eb755bbda8","tid":1928832,"uid":78039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"示威者應該跟中共學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時搞事最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63874343fc6f16e1f793a260421fe582525bc02c","tid":1928832,"uid":85169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d5d65ac9ba4bc0729c96e5b297ae7eb755bbda8","tid":1928832,"uid":78039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"示威者應該跟中共學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時搞事最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:33:40.000Z","msg":"咁趁人病攞人命係最有效，<br />\n所以以家應該係要大事宣傳叫人唔好幫襯藍店"}]}